                     <interp inst="t17820703-23-person193" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>I am servant to Mr. Dolman. I saw the prisoner come into the shop, and take the cloth off the counter. I ran out after him, and cried, Stop thief! and Mr. Locke stopped him.</p>
               <p>
                  <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="178207030012"></xptr>(The cloth was produced in court, and deposed to by the prosecutor.)</p>
               <p>PRISONER's DEFENCE.</p>
               <p>I am innocent. I never had the cloth.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17820703-23-verdict98" type="verdictDescription">
